name: Curious Peek
description:
A Black-Capped Chickadee peeks out from behind a lichen covered branch curiously after carefully stashing seeds.

2017. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.

Birb Series: Part 1 - Chickadee II
